          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The absolute normalization of cross",
                "sections was obtained by measuring deuteron elastic",
                "scattering simultaneously in the counter experiment and",
                "normalizing it to the optical model predictions for the",
                "same. Excitation energies were determined from the",
                "spectrograph experiment.",
                "The relative cross sections measured in the counter",
                "experiment were normalized to the optical model",
                "predictions to yield the absolute cross section",
                "normalization."
              ]
            }
          ],
